      "user": "holdenreviews",
      "slug": "minimalist-cinema",
      "title": "Minimalist Cinema",
      "desc": "Not a lot going on here...\nBut seriously, I love minimalist cinema. It's so hypnotic and stuff. For this list, I'm not using a set definition, but I'm choosing films that utilize one or more of the following: minimal plot, minimal characters. minimal locations, minimal dialogue.\nSuggestions welcome.",
